               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus” (fols. 2ra-52vb)
 I-1)
                     ʾƎsaggǝd la-malakotǝka... “I worship Thy Godhead…” (fols. 2ra-4rb)
 I-2)
                     Introduction (fols. 5ra-16rb)
 - On John the Evangelist as the author of
                     the book; on the creation and the fall of the angels (fols. 5ra-10ra)
 -
                     Story of the family of Adam (fols. 10ra-16rb)
 I-3) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus
                     “Miracles of Jesus”: 15 miracles (fols. 16rb-52vb), incomplete [continuation of
                     the text is in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESamm006">AMM-006</ref>]
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
